]%.\nConclusions: The high spatial resolution experimental dosimetry technique based\non Raman micro-spectroscopy and RCF presented here, could become useful for\napplications in, as well as for applications based on small field dosimetry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 20:46:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
