l achieves similar\ncontrast recovery coefficients as MLEM except for the smallest structures where\nthe low-count nature of the simulations makes it difficult to draw conclusions.\nHowever, this new model seems to converge toward less noisy solutions than\nMLEM. These results suggest that the PADE approach has potential for low-count\nreconstruction with ultra-fast TOF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 May 2021 03:39:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2023 19:39:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-12"}
