ied and generalized parametrization definition of\nan anti-crossing in the context of quantum optimization annealing introduced in\n[4].\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 May 2021 15:21:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2022 23:03:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-28"}
