's do not fulfill the prediction of SLE\nfor the relation between $D_f(H)$ and the diffusivity parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 19:57:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-16"}
